  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>BEFORE BUYING THE GAME:</u> THIS IS A JUMPSCARES BASED GAME, DON'T EXPECT A STORY OR PLOT. TEST YOUR LIMITS AND TRY NOT TO MAKE ANY NOISE INTO THE MICROPHONE WHILE EXPLORING HAUNTED LOCATIONS. CALL YOUR FRIENDS TO PLAY, YOUR FAMILY... YOUR PARENTS, SERIOUSLY... THIS WILL BE FUN!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/9690392095f38b4510635f3f508df68c.webp?t=1744102957\" width=600 height=35 /></span><strong>SHHH!</strong> is a terrifying horror experience where your worst enemy... is yourself! Stay silent, or the nightmare begins again! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔇 <strong>Microphone required</strong> – The game listens to you! Make a noise or scream, and it's game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📹 Explore eerie, haunted locations through the lens of your VHS camera.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳ <strong>Survive for <u>10 minutes</u></strong> without making a sound… Think you can handle it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/274281936cb890616c18be6a1fc8d082.webp?t=1744102957\" width=600 height=35 /></span><strong>Immersive Horror Like Never Before</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎙️ <strong>Microphone-based gameplay</strong> – A good mic and headset are essential for the full experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/9dc60b7f5016aff0b755567709d86c22.webp?t=1744102957\" width=600 height=35 /></span><strong>Thre unique scenarios</strong> – Each with its own chilling atmosphere and unexpected horrors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BARBACENA ASYLUM</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MORGAN'S HOUSE</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WITCH FOREST</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/b6f07ef300aaa57eb520d1bef549e956.webp?t=1744102957\" width=600 height=35 /></span>🚶 <strong>A true walking simulator</strong> – No puzzles, no interactions—just you, the darkness, and whatever lurks within…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play alone. Lights off. Stay quiet… or face the consequences.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/d6f7cef6b73cdacb7a9a3b2ae940e804.poster.avif?t=1744102957\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/d6f7cef6b73cdacb7a9a3b2ae940e804.webm?t=1744102957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/d6f7cef6b73cdacb7a9a3b2ae940e804.mp4?t=1744102957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/7786e0a9b931799a1e255b4a37609d58.avif?t=1744102957\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1744102957\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1744102957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709940/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1744102957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
